com.github.yona168.giraffe.net.packet

Class QueuedOpSendablePacket

  • com.github.yona168.giraffe.net.packet.QueuedOpSendablePacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SendablePacket

    public class QueuedOpSendablePacket
implements SendablePacket

    An implementation of interface SendablePacket that queues writing operations until building. This allows for multiple builds of a packet as well as easy ability to prepend information. This implementation builds a packet as follows:

    1. The opcode of the packet (of type Opcode).

    2. The size of the packet (of type Size).

    3. The rest of the bytes.

    See Also:
    interface SendablePacket
